<parameter name="new_string">    category: 'research',
    helpText: 'A geriatric case manager specializes in navigating the complex healthcare system and coordinating multiple providers to create cohesive care plans. They can assess your parent\'s current needs, identify service gaps, coordinate between doctors and specialists, and help implement sustainable care strategies. This professional coordination becomes essential as care needs increase and helps prevent medical errors while ensuring all providers are working toward unified care goals.'
