    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Technology solutions can significantly enhance your parent\'s safety, independence, and social connections when chosen and set up thoughtfully. Work with your parent to evaluate their comfort level with devices, then implement solutions like voice-activated assistants for medication reminders, video calling for family connections, or smart home devices for safety monitoring. Focus on simple, reliable technologies that enhance rather than complicate their daily routines.'
  }
